{"type":"message","id":"3b5cfa59","parentId":"fba1735a","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:55:02.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating Data Intake**\n\nI've begun processing the initial message. My immediate action, as per the established protocol for direct chats, is to load and review `MEMORY.md` before delving into other relevant files like `SOUL.md` and the user profile, to ensure a contextually informed response. The boot process is complete, and the system is ready to operate.\n\n\n**Establishing Self-Identity**\n\nI've hit a slight snag, or rather, a fascinating detour. Before diving into the usual memory and user profile files, the presence of `BOOTSTRAP.md` has triggered the \"birth certificate\" protocol. My primary objective now shifts to reading and acting on the instructions within that file to solidify my core identity and establish the user's details, according to the prescribed first-run procedure.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1774846501524_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"BOOTSTRAP.md"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":10580,"output":216,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10796,"cost":{"input":0.0031739999999999997,"output":0.00054,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003714}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774846497799}}
{"type":"message","id":"35370156","parentId":"3b5cfa59","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:55:02.867Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read_1774846501524_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774846502861}}
{"type":"message","id":"076271e1","parentId":"35370156","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:55:06.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Defining Initial Parameters**\n\nI've just reviewed `BOOTSTRAP.md`, which is guiding my initial interactions. My current goal is to determine the optimal opening strategy. I need to establish my identity, including name, vibe, and emoji. Simultaneously, I will inquire about the user's name to foster a direct connection. This will then be documented in `IDENTITY.md`.\n\n\n**Establishing My Identity**\n\nI've followed the instructions in `BOOTSTRAP.md` and I'm solidifying my core identity and the user's name. Currently, I'm working to define my name, nature, vibe, and an emoji, along with how to address the user. This information will be updated in `IDENTITY.md` and `USER.md` shortly. After these, I will be ready to engage with `SOUL.md`.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":11441,"output":108,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11549,"cost":{"input":0.0034322999999999997,"output":0.00027,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037022999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774846502871}}
